Thank you for your interest in Dassault Systèmes.

Kind regards,
3DS Talent Acquisition & Mobility

messages.messageText:
Hi, Tata Social Enterprise Challenge 2025 is back with its 13th edition. Tata Social Enterprise Challenge (TSEC) is an annual competition that aims to identify and support social entrepreneurs who are creating sustainable and scalable solutions to address some of India's most pressing social problems. Social entrepreneurs identified through the competition receive mentorship support, cash prizes, can pitch for funding to TSEC seed fund & impact investors and get incubation at IIM Calcutta Innovation Park (IIMCIP). Is this something which interests you? Participate in this one-of-a-kind social entrepreneurship challenge by visiting the website IIMCIP Contest Portal. To know more, visit the website: https://www.tatasechallenge.org/ and you can also click on 'Apply now,' it will redirect you to the same link mentioned above. It's your time to shine. All the best ! Thanks and Regards Careers@TCS Tata Consultancy Services =====-----=====-----===== Notice: The information contained in this e-mail message and/or attachments to it may contain confidential or privileged information. If you are not the intended recipient, any dissemination, use, review, distribution, printing or copying of the information contained in this e-mail message and/or attachments to it are strictly prohibited. If you have received this communication in error, please notify us by reply e-mail or telephone and immediately and permanently delete the message and any attachments. Thank you Hi,

Tata Social Enterprise Challenge 2025 is back with its 13th edition. Tata Social Enterprise Challenge (TSEC) is an annual competition that aims to identify and support social entrepreneurs who are creating sustainable and scalable solutions to address some of India's most pressing social problems. Social entrepreneurs identified through the competition receive mentorship support, cash prizes, can pitch for funding to TSEC seed fund & impact investors and get incubation at IIM Calcutta Innovation Park (IIMCIP). 
 
Is this something which interests you?
Participate in this one-of-a-kind social entrepreneurship challenge by visiting the website IIMCIP Contest Portal.
To know more, visit the website: https://www.tatasechallenge.org/ and you can also click on 'Apply now,' it will redirect you to the same link mentioned above.  



It's your time to shine. All the best !


Thanks and Regards
Careers@TCS
Tata Consultancy Services

messages.messageText:
Dear Abhinav,

Your account has been locked after an unsuccessful authentication procedure. To unlock your account, access our Career Section login page, click "Forgot your password?", and follow the instructions.

We also invite you to view the list of all current job openings within our organization and visit regularly our career website.

Thank you for your interest in Dassault Systèmes.

Kind regards,
3DS Talent Acquisition & Mobility
Dassault Systèmes
 
This message is sent from a computer system that hasn’t yet figured out how to read and reply to messages. One day it will come; until then, please do not reply to this email.

This email is an automated notification.
This email and any attachments are intended solely for the use of the individual or entity to whom it is addressed and may be confidential and/or privileged.
If you are not one of the named recipients or have received this email in error,
(i) you should not read, disclose, or copy it,
(ii) please notify sender of your receipt by reply email and delete this email and all attachments,
